<emphasis italics="true" pageId="176" pageNumber="177">Aucher-Eloy</emphasis>
1397); Iran (
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="176" pageNumber="177">Kotschy</emphasis>
436, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="176" pageNumber="177">Hewer</emphasis>
3997, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="176" pageNumber="177">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bornmüller">Bornmueller</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
3883, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="176" pageNumber="177">Bokhari &amp; Edmondson</emphasis>
2087); Afghanistan (
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="176" pageNumber="177">Gibbons</emphasis>
457). This subspecies has a more eastern distribution than 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="subsp. dorycnium" order="Solanales" pageId="176" pageNumber="177" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="dorycnium" subSpecies="dorycnium">subsp. dorycnium</taxonomicName>
